“It is true this is a difficult time and we urge the media to at least give us positive coverage as we marshal our players to come back for training. The issue at hand which is salary payment is being sorted by the management of the club,” said Obondo.
As the K’Ogalo camp remained in turmoil CR Belouizdad quietly landed in Nairobi Sunday at 7pm.
